e rescued the raped gill. DSP Adhikari said the girl was rescued acting on the allegation that the school teacher and rural municipality employee have been frequently raping the adolescent.\n\n\n\n\u201cWe are minutely investigating the case. We are also trying to understand the rape survivor. None involved in such crime would go scot free\u201d, DSP Adhikari said.\n\n\n\nThe rape case has come to the public after the married adolescent delivered a child in six months following her wedding.","title":"Baitadi: Rape-accused held, adolescent rescued","url":"http://www.nayapage.com/archives/262687","video":[]}
